'''Fred Swaniker''' (1976) ni rwiyemezamirimo wo muri [[Gana]] akaba n'inzobere mu iterambere ry'ubuyobozi. Yatangije imiryango ine igamije guteza imbere abayobozi, cyane cyane muri Afrika. Niwe washinze  ishuri rikuru rya African Leadership Academy na kaminuza ya [[Afurika|Afrika]] y'Ubuyobozi ifite icyicaro i Kigali, mu Rwanda. Niwe kandi washinze umuyoboro nyafurika wo kuyobora hamwe na [https://www.experiencegla.com/ Global Leadership Adventures] .

== Ubuzimwa bwe bwahambere  ==
Se ni umunyamategeko n'umucamanza. Afite imyaka ine, byabaye ngombwa ko ahunga [[Gana]] nyuma yo guhirika ubutegetsi . Mbere yimyaka cumi n'umunani avutse, yabaga mubihugu bine bya Afrika <ref>https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p04j9syx</ref> . Amashuri ye yayize muri Macalester College muri Minnesota . Nyuma yaje gukora mu kigo ngishwanama cya McKinsey & Company i Johannesburg mbere yo gukora impamyabumenyi ya MBA i Stanford, muri Californiya . Arangije amasomo ye, yamenyekanye cyane nka Arjay Miller Scholar amumenya ko ari mu 10% ba mbere mu itsinda ry’abanyeshuri beza mu ishuri rye.

Ishuri ryigisha ubuyobozi nubuhanga bwo kwihangira imirimo kubanyeshuri baturutse muri [[Afurika|Afrika]] yose, kubategurira no kwiga kaminuza. . Kuva muri 2017, abayobozi bagera ku 1.000 bazaza mu ishuri. Ku banyeshuri benshi, amafaranga y'ishuri avanwaho kugira ngo basezerane gukorera muri Afurika nyuma y'amasomo yabo <ref name="Barret">https://www.forbes.com/2008/05/23/africa-brain-drain-tech-ebiz-cz_vb_0526africa.html?sh=3bee758814c7</ref> .

Muri 2014, mu nama ya TED yabereye muri Berezile, Swaniker yatangaje ko yaguye icyerekezo cye: umuyoboro mushya wa kaminuza 25 zo muri Afurika uzahugura abayobozi miliyoni 3 muri 2060 <ref>https://www.lemonde.fr/afrique/article/2015/11/06/fred-swaniker-nous-construisons-l-universite-du-futur-en-afrique_4804731_3212.html</ref> , <ref>https://www.jeuneafrique.com/277371/economie/fred-swaniker-le-secteur-prive-peut-aider-lafrique-a-entrer-dans-leconomie-mondiale-du-savoir/</ref> , <ref>https://lesclesdedemain.lemonde.fr/economie/fred-swaniker-pour-sortir-de-la-pauvrete-en-afrique-il-faut-investir-dans-nos-cerveaux-_a-90-5604.html</ref> .

Kuva mu 2016 hafunguwe ibigo bibiri : imwe muri Maurice naho iya kabiri mu Rwanda muri [[Kigali]] . Ikinyamakuru cyo muri Amerika cyihuta cyagaragaje uyu muyoboro w’ishuri na kaminuza nkimwe mu masosiyete agezweho muri Afurika. Byongeye kandi, itangazamakuru CNN ryerekanye uyu mushinga nka Havard yo muri Afurika <ref>https://www.bbc.com/worklife/article/20190718-fred-swaniker</ref> , <ref>https://edition.cnn.com/2016/09/06/africa/fred-swaniker-teacher-leadership-africa/index.html</ref> .

Graca Machel wahoze ari Minisitiri w’uburezi muri Mozambike akaba n’umupfakazi wa Nelson Mandela, yabaye umuyobozi wa kaminuza naho [[Donald Kaberuka]] wahoze ari Perezida wa Banki Nyafurika itsura amajyambere, ari mu nama y’ubuyobozi.

== Umwuga ==
